**Plan for USS content:**
```css
:root {
    --bg-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); /* Transparent */
    --bar-bg: #333;
    --bar-fill: #aaa;
    --text-color: white;
    --icon-size: 45px;
}

.hud-root {
    flex-grow: 1;
    width: 1920px;
    height: 1080px;
}

.top-section {
    height: 240px;
    padding: 20px;
    flex-direction: column;
}

.bottom-section {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    height: 240px;
    padding: 20px;
    flex-direction: column;
}

.label-text {
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

/* HP Bar */
.hp-container {
    height: 30px;
    background-color: var(--bar-bg);
    border-width: 1px;
    border-color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.hp-fill {
    width: 60%; /* Example fill */
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--bar-fill);
}

/* Rows */
.row {
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
}

.spell-row, .rune-row {
    gap: 10px;
}

/* Icons */
.icon {
    width: var(--icon-size);
    height: var(--icon-size);
    border-radius: 22px; /* Half of size */
    background-color: #222;
    border-width: 2px;
    border-color: #777;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
}

.icon-text {
    color: white;
    font-size: 14px;
}
```

